My Curly Hair Routine 🍍 Don't forget to Tag your curly hair buddies 🌴
Products used: 
I Start off in the shower with OGX coconut miracle oil Shampoo and Conditioner #ogx #coconutoilshampoo @ogxbeautyuk. Then i protect my hair against any heat that will be used with Heat protection spray by #tresemme @tresemmearabia. To protect my hair from the humidity and to keep it soft throughout the day I use a little bit of Argan oil by Pura D'or #PuraD'or #arganoil #arganoil. And finally i use Elvive Extraordinary Oil by @lorealprome @lorealparisrd. After than i wait for 20 minutes for the top part to dry and fix the curls with a curling iron, putting it on the lowest heat setting. I hope you guys enjoyed it. #dubailife #dubaimakeupartist #curlyhair #curlyhairroutine #curlyhairproducts #hudabeauty #hudabeautyinspiration #wakeupandmakeup

_source.main:
I have dyed my hair 3 weeks ago and it made it dry. I found this hair treatment Oil from @lorealprome called Extraordinary Oil made of 6  oil essences. There were 2 or 3 types. I took this one because it was for colored hair😜
It did add life and smoothness to my hair. It's not very greasy and easily gone from hair once washed with shampoo. I apply it with massage on my scalp then lightly over entire hair and leave it for 30-60 minutes and then washed.
I don't recall the exact price but I think it was around 6 O.R.
قبل ٣ أسابيع صبغت شعري و الصبغة شوي نشفت شعري فلقيت هالزيت في السوبرماركت من لوريال. عبارة عن ٦ زيوت مستخلصة من زهور نادرة و هذا خاص بالشعر المصبوغ و في نوعين او ثلاثة ثانيين . الحلو فيه ان يطلع لسهولة من الشعر اول ما ينغسل بالشامبو.
أنا أدلك فيه فروة راسي وبعدين أحطه على خفيف على باقي شعري و أخليه من نص ساعة لحد ساعة و بعدين اغسله. 
حسيته رجع الحياة بشعري و خفف الجفاف .
سعره ما أتذكره بالضبط بس بحدود ال٦ ريالات عمانية.
